snippet: Iran's non-oil exports are starting to feel the benefits of easing international tensions under new President Hassan Rouhani, Iranian businessmen at one of the world's biggest food industry shows say....

headline.print_headline: Iran's Non-Oil Exports Recovering Under Rouhani, Business Says
headline.main: Iran's Non-Oil Exports Recovering Under Rouhani, Business Says

lead_paragraph: Iran's non-oil exports are starting to feel the benefits of easing international tensions under new President Hassan Rouhani, Iranian businessmen at one of the world's biggest food industry shows say.
